data.description: LOTS of house for a GREAT price. Seller would like this one sold quickly & is agreeable to a painting allowance with an acceptable offer. Check out this 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom home located in the Ridge Creek neighborhood, just minutes from FLW and in the Waynesville school district. Enter through the covered front porch into the living room with laminate flooring. The kitchen shows beautiful light oak cabinetry, some stainless appliances, red laminate counter tops, moveable island and a breakfast bar. There is no shortage of cabinet and countertop space! The master bedroom suite features carpet flooring, cathedral style ceiling, huge walk in closet & attached master bathroom suite. Master bath includes his & her sinks, sliding glass door shower & a soaking tub. There are two other guest bedrooms and a guest bathroom upstairs as well. The basement has two more guest bedrooms, a full bathroom and LARGE family room area with fireplace. If you need space, you've found it here!
